Sentencas: Driven by the mounting concerns on global warming and energy crisis, intermediate temperature solid-oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) have attracted special attention for their high fuel efficiency, low toxic gas emission, and great fuel flexibility.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: A key obstacle to the practical operation of IT-SOFCs is their sluggish oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) kinetics.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In this work, we applied a new two-layered Ruddlesden-Popper (R-P) oxide, Sr3Fe2O7-delta (SFO), as the material for oxygen ion conducting IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Density functional theory calculation suggested that SFO has extremely low oxygen ion formation energy and considerable energy barrier for O2- diffusion.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Unfortunately, the stable SrO surface of SFO was demonstrated to be inert to O-2 adsorption and dissociation reaction, and thus restricts its catalytic activity toward ORR Based on this observation, Co partially substituted SFO (SFCO) was then synthesized and applied to improve its surface vacancy concentration to accelerate the oxygen adsorptive reduction reaction rate.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical performance results suggested that the cell using the SFCO single phase cathode has a peak power density of 685 mW cm(-2) at 650 degrees C, about 15% higher than those when using LSCF cathode.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Operating at 200 mA cm(-2), the new cell using SFCO is quite stable within the 100-h' test.
Titulo: High-Performanced Cathode with a Two-Layered R-P Structure for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
